  item:
    itemName: Radio
    requestTags:
    - Noise
    - Connection
    - Distraction
    consequenceLines: []
    statTag: Self
    value: 10
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - It only works if you hit it a little.
    - "Most of the time it\u2019s just static or quiet voices."
    - I used to leave it on while doing homework.
    - "Sometimes I think I hear songs I recognize, but I\u2019m not sure."
    - "It sounds better when you\u2019re not paying attention."
