    - Authority
    consequenceLines:
    - couch gone
    statTag: Family
    value: 10
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - Dad always sits here after dinner.
    - It makes a loud sound when you move it even a little.
    - "It smells like him, even when he\u2019s not here."
    - Nobody else really sits in it.
    - "It feels like it\u2019s waiting for someone...not any of us."
