    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - "We\u2019re supposed to make sure this lasts the whole week."
    - Dad gets annoyed when I take too much.
    - I remember what we had last time we ran out.
    - "I think this is the kind of thing you\u2019re not supposed to waste."
    - "Sometimes there\u2019s not enough, but nobody says it out loud."
