    - bottle gone
    statTag: Family
    value: 10
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - Dads getting stressed with everything.
    - "There\u2019s always at least one of these around somewhere."
    - "Dad doesn\u2019t really say much when it\u2019s out."
    - It smells strong if you get too close.
    - "Sometimes it\u2019s empty, sometimes it isn\u2019t."
    - "I\u2019m not really supposed to touch it, so I don\u2019t."
