  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  item:
    itemName: Sticky Note
    requestTags:
    - Information
    - Memory
    - Reminder
    consequenceLines: []
    statTag: Family
    value: 10
    sacrificeWeight: 0
    descriptions:
    - There used to be a bunch of these stuck on the fridge.
    - "Mom writes things like \u2018don\u2019t forget\u2019 on these."
    - "I never know if I\u2019m supposed to read them or not."
    - I'm surprised. Most of these fall off and end up on the floor.
